	[em 
		"Super Adventure Rockman
	]em
	" is an interactive anime FMV movie and one of the few 
	[em 
		"Mega Man
	]em
	" games that were released only in Japan. Most of the gameplay involves choosing decisions for Mega Man and his allies as they progress through the story, with rail shooter sequences every couple of minutes to add variety. As for the story, Dr. Wily discovers a supercomputer, in an ancient ruin, that can revive as well as disable technology all over the world, and uses it to hold the world's robot population hostage. Thankfully, Dr. Light manages to make Mega Man and a few of his allies immune to the supercomputer's effect. It's up to Mega Man to stop Dr. Wily before the power he unleashes could prove disastrous to the entire world.
